name: Healthcare and Social Services Statistics (Socialstyrelsen)
description: Statistical databases with data on abortions, acute myocardial infarctions, cancer, causes of death, health care practitioners, in-patient care diagnoses, pharmaceuticals, elderly care, social assistance, and related healthcare and social services topics. Data is presented by year, gender, age, and geographical area.
owner_name: Socialstyrelsen (National Board of Health and Welfare)
